{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/string-no-newline/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/function-calc-no-unspaced-operator/","description":"function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction 禁止在 linear-gradient() 中调用不符合标准语法的无效方向值。 有效的标准方向值是以下之一： 一个角度 to 加上一个方位（to top、to bottom、to…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction\"><a href=\"#function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction</h1>\n<p>禁止在 <code>linear-gradient()</code> 中调用不符合<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/linear-gradient#%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\">标准语法</a>的无效方向值。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(to top, #fff, #000); }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**                                ↑\n *                  这第一个参数（可选）是“方向” */</span></code></pre>\n<p>有效的标准方向值是以下之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>一个角度</li>\n<li><code>to</code> 加上一个方位（<code>to top</code>、<code>to bottom</code>、<code>to left</code>、<code>to right</code>；<code>to top right</code>, <code>to right top</code>、<code>to bottom left</code> 等等。）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一个常见的错误（匹配过时的非标准语法）是只使用一个前面没有 <code>to</code> 的方位。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(top, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(bottom, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(left, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(45, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(to top top, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(to top, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(to bottom right, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(45deg, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(1.57rad, #fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 方向默认为 \"to bottom\" */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">linear-gradient</span>(#fff, #000); }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/function-linear-gradient-no-nonstandard-direction/index.html.780222132c3eadacede7a50c7ab2ce7e.json"}